data.name: PubChem_DTXSID_mapping_file.txt
data.label: DSSTox Identifier to PubChem Identifier Mapping File
data.title: DSSTox Identifier to PubChem Identifier Mapping File
data.longDescription: The DSSTox to PubChem Identifiers mapping file is in TXT format and includes the PubChem SID, PubChem CID and DSSTox substance identifier (DTXSID).

data.name: Dsstox_CAS_number_name.xlsx
data.label: DSSTox identifiers mapped to CAS Numbers and Names File
data.title: DSSTox identifiers mapped to CAS Numbers and Names File
data.longDescription: The DSSTox Identifiers file is in Excel format and includes the CAS Number, DSSTox substance identifier (DTXSID), Preferred Name, DTXCID. Standard InChI String and Standard InChIKey (UPDATED APRIL 2019).
